<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Jon_Krakauer" title="Jon Krakauer">Krakauer, Jon.</a> <i><a href="/wiki/Under_the_Banner_of_Heaven:_A_Story_of_Violent_Faith" class="mw-redirect" title="Under the Banner of Heaven: A Story of Violent Faith">Under the Banner of Heaven: A Story of Violent Faith</a></i> (2003).</li>
