<li>Bistline, Benjamin G. <i>The Polygamists: A History of Colorado City, Arizona</i> (2004)</li>
<li>Tracy, Kathleen. <i>The Secret Story of Polygamy</i> (2001). Centered on the trial of John Daniel Kingston, who was tried for assault on his 16-year-old daughter.</li>
