<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFDan_SimonAmanda_Townsend2007" class="citation news cs1">Dan Simon &amp; Amanda Townsend (September 7, 2007). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.cnn.com/2007/US/09/07/lost.boys/index.html">"Warren Jeffs' 'lost boys' find themselves in strange world"</a>. <a href="/wiki/CNN" title="CNN">CNN</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Warren+Jeffs%27+%27lost+boys%27+find+themselves+in+strange+world&amp;rft.date=2007-09-07&amp;rft.au=Dan+Simon&amp;rft.au=Amanda+Townsend&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2007%2FUS%2F09%2F07%2Flost.boys%2Findex.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALost+boys+%28Mormon+fundamentalism%29" class="Z3988"></span></li>
